g-munro-scotland-sunset-696x465.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/sean-green-grizzly-munro-descending-munro-scotland-sunset-1068x713.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/sean-green-grizzly-munro-descending-munro-scotland-sunset-629x420.jpg 629w\"></a></p><p><em>Those are the days I yearn for, the slithers of golden singletrack never before ridden, are just a bonus”.</em></p><p>Hit the link below to follow Sean on his mission to bag all 282 Munros.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFmdysZ-M92aE3n3y-p4XWQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>GrizzlyMunroDiaries.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"177fc9e989b0e63369dc0eccaa83bca0de38c7e30afc1f0a2455484b10bb3362","category":"Cycling"}